meta {
  name: GET charging history (v1.15.0, #35 closer)
  type: http
  seq: 5
}

get {
  url: {{base_url}}/api/v1/charging/{{vin}}/history?userTimezone=UTC&limit=50
  body: none
  auth: bearer
}

auth:bearer {
  token: {{access_token}}
}

headers {
  Accept: application/json
}

docs {
  v1.15.0 (#35 Ladehistorie LTS closer) — Skoda Charging History.
  Drives sensor.total_charged_energy_kwh (TOTAL_INCREASING) for HA
  Energy Dashboard plus 2 last-session sensors plus
  recent_charging_sessions as extra_state_attributes.

  Response shape: {nextCursor, periods: [{totalChargedInKWh,
  sessions: [{startAt, chargedInKWh, durationInMinutes,
  currentType: AC|DC}]}]}

  Verified against myskoda/models/charging_history.py.
  Implementation: SkodaClient.get_charging_history() in
  custom_components/vag_connect/cariad/api/skoda.py.
  Coordinator: refresh_charging_history() — 1h cache, brand-restricted.
}
